ertrug Popper diese Gedanken auf die Sozialwissenschaften und die politische Philosophie. Der vorliegende Sammelband übernimmt im wesentlichen die Gliederung der 'Logik der Forschung'. Seine Beiträge kommentieren die jeweiligen Themen gemäß dem heutigen Stand der Forschung.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh1 aAndersson, Gunnar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBühler, Axel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDüsberg, Klaus Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGadenne, Volker, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKeuth, Herbert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKeuth, Herbert, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMiller, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMusgrave, Alan E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchroeder-Heister, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchurz, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSimon, Herbert A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWendel, Hans Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZahar, Elie G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket AV  Philosophie 2005-2012z9783110347067oZDB-74-AKP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305005018840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050050188423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050050188.jpg 